      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.izwXGb47fdrQ8qQw]{Immortal Tutor (Su) - Fiend}</p>\n<p>When you cast a 1st-level or higher technomancer spell, you can gain the tutor’s first lesson for a number of rounds equal to your Intelligence modifier. After you do so, you can’t use the first lesson again until you have rested 10 minutes to regain Stamina Points.</p>\n<p><strong>First Lesson:</strong> You gain DR/evil with a value equal to 1-1/2 × the spell’s level (rounded down).</p>\n<p><em>DR must be edited in the Modifiers tab to match the calculation result.</em></p>"
